233struct animinfo
234{
235 int anim, frame, range, basetime;
236 float speed;
237 uint varseed;
238
239 animinfo() : anim(0), frame(0), range(0), basetime(0), speed(100.0f), varseed(0) { }
240
241 bool operator==(const animinfo &o) const
242 {
243 return frame==o.frame && range==o.range && (anim&(Anim_SetTime | Anim_Dir)) == (o.anim & (Anim_SetTime | Anim_Dir)) && (anim & Anim_SetTime || basetime == o.basetime) && speed == o.speed;
244 }
245 bool operator!=(const animinfo &o) const
246 {
247 return frame!=o.frame || range!=o.range || (anim&(Anim_SetTime | Anim_Dir)) != (o.anim & (Anim_SetTime | Anim_Dir)) || (!(anim & Anim_SetTime) && basetime != o.basetime) || speed != o.speed;
248 }
249};

281 ~dynent()

286 cleanragdoll(this);
287 }
288 }
289
290 void stopmoving()
291 {
292 k_left = k_right = k_up = k_down = jumping = false;
293 move = strafe = crouching = 0;
294 }
295
296 void reset()
297 {
298 physent::reset();
299 stopmoving();
300 for(int i = 0; i < maxanimparts; ++i)
301 {
302 animinterp[i].reset();
303 }
304 }
